---
---
<section id="rubrica" class="rubrica-section reveal">
  <div class="bg-decorations">
    <div class="radial radial-1"></div>
    <div class="radial radial-2"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="rubrica-grid">
      <div class="rubrica-left">
        <span class="eyebrow grad-text">Cómo funciona el sistema</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          La norma deja de ser un PDF. Empieza a ser una <em class="grad-text">conversación</em>.
        </h2>
        <p class="lede">
          AgentNexus orquesta cuatro agentes especializados que trabajan en cadena: el Enrutador analiza tu intención, el Documentalista extrae la norma exacta, el Agente de Procesos te guía paso a paso, y el Sintetizador redacta la respuesta final con cita verificada.
        </p>

        <ul class="rubrica-list mono">
          <li><strong>Agente Enrutador</strong> — analiza la intención y despacha al agente especialista correcto.</li>
          <li><strong>Agente Documentalista</strong> — extrae artículos exactos del corpus vectorial sin inventar nada.</li>
          <li><strong>Agente de Procesos</strong> — guía al usuario paso a paso en trámites operativos.</li>
          <li><strong>Agente Sintetizador</strong> — redacta la respuesta final, verificada y citada.</li>
          <li><strong>Escalabilidad modular</strong> — agentes drop-in. Cualquier institución adopta el copiloto cambiando solo el corpus.</li>
        </ul>

        <a href="/roles" class="btn-primary cta-enter">
          <span class="dot pulse"></span>
          Probar el copiloto →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="rubrica-right">
        <div class="terminal">
          <div class="term-header">
            <div class="dots">
              <span class="dot-btn close"></span>
              <span class="dot-btn min"></span>
              <span class="dot-btn max"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="term-title mono">~/agentnexus · main</div>
          </div>
          <div class="term-body mono">
            <div class="line"><span class="prompt">$</span> python ingest.py --source ./docs/</div>
            <div class="line dim">&gt; parsing PDFs · chunking by article · embedding…</div>
            <div class="line"><span class="success">✓</span> 1,284 chunks · vector store ready</div>
            <br/>
            <div class="line"><span class="prompt">$</span> rasa train && rasa run --enable-api</div>
            <div class="line"><span class="success">✓</span> rasa NLU · 4 intents · enrutador / documentalista / procesos / sintetizador</div>
            <div class="line"><span class="success">✓</span> langgraph router online</div>
            <br/>
            <div class="line"><span class="prompt">$</span> gradio app.py</div>
            <div class="line"><span class="success">✓</span> copiloto listening on http://localhost:7860</div>
            <br/>
            <div class="line"><span class="user-msg">user</span> "¿Puedo solicitar una equivalencia sin haber aprobado el 50% de créditos?"</div>
            <div class="line"><span class="bot-msg">→</span> Reglamento Académico · Art. 42 · párrafo 1 <span class="success">[✓ verificado]</span></div>
            <br/>
            <div class="line"><span class="prompt">$</span><span class="cursor blink"></span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .rubrica-section {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: white;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bg-decorations {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .radial {
    position: absolute;
    width: 800px;
    height: 800px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(229, 92, 50, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .radial-1 { top: -200px; right: -200px; }
  .radial-2 { bottom: -400px; left: -100px; }

  .content-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: var(--max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--gutter);
  }

  .rubrica-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    color: white;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 32rem;
  }

  .rubrica-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .rubrica-list li {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .rubrica-list li::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--coral-500);
  }
  .rubrica-list strong {
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--coral-600);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--coral-500);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .terminal {
    background: #07070A;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .term-header {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .dot-btn {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .dot-btn.close { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
  .dot-btn.min { background: var(--coral-300); }
  .dot-btn.max { background: var(--coral-500); }

  .term-title {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  .term-body {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  }

  .line { margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
  .prompt { color: var(--coral-400); margin-right: 0.5rem; }
  .dim { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }
  .success { color: #4ADE80; margin-right: 0.5rem; }
  .user-msg { color: var(--signal); font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0.5rem; }
  .bot-msg { color: var(--coral-500); font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0.5rem; }
  
  .cursor {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 8px;
    height: 1em;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    vertical-align: middle;
    margin-left: 0.2rem;
  }
  .cursor.blink {
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .rubrica-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
